// ============================= MASTER BLOCK =========================
Name Halloween_11_Trial
FirstStage Setup
StopStage Stop
RestartStage Setup
DisplayName P2023463106
// --------------------------------------------------------------------

// ======================== STAGE DESCRIPTIONS ======================== 
//Stage 0  - Prelude - Players arrive at the mansion, get a story hit, objective is to enter the mansion.
//Stage 1 - Mansion - Players enter the mansion, get a quick story hit, objective is to find Dr. Kane.
//Stage 2 - MansionBossRoom - Players locate Dr. Kane, he monologues and raises zombies, objective is to kill zombies and then rolls to exit the mansion.
//Stage 3 - Tombs - Players follow Dr. Kane, enter the tombs, objective is to follow Dr. Kane.
//Stage 4 - TombBossRoom - Players once again catch up with Dr. Kane, he monologues again (like any good villain would), raises a zombie, objective is to kill Experiment Number Nine and then rolls to exit the tombs.
//Stage 5 - Graveyard - Players enter the graveyard where Dr. Kane delivers his final monologue before raising the Abominaiton, objective is to kill the Abomination.
//Stage 6 - Rewards - Issues rewards, starts a 5 minute timer. After this point moves to the stop stage.
//Stage 7 - Stop - Parks the event, cleans up spawns.
// --------------------------------------------------------------------

