			DoorCreate Door-Mansion2 //Add the following property to the MapSwap: Halloween_11_Trial.Door.Door-Mansion2 zoneevent>
			DoorCreate Door-TombExit //Add the following property to the MapSwap: Halloween_11_Trial.Door.Door-TombExit zoneevent>

